General Information

Satisfy your sweet tooth with our delicious Choc Coconut Protein Puds with chia! Packed with the goodness of chia, cocoa & a hint of coconut, they are gluten-free, a good source of protein, calcium and fibre and are only 111 calories. The lid even includes a spoon so you're ready to satisfy that sweet craving when and where it strikes. But don't take our word for it... the proof is in the pudding!

Gluten free
Good source of protein
Good source of calcium
Good source of fibre
Low fat
No artificial colours, flavours or sweeteners
No added preservatives
No GMO ingredients

Warnings

Contain milk

Common Uses

Between meals as a snack option, after a workout for a protein boost, a low cal. Low carb dessert or used as part of a recipe

Ingredients

Water, Milk Solids, Thickeners (1442, 415), Dietary Fibre (Inulin), Desiccated Coconut (2%), Cocoa (1.7%), Natural Flavours, Sugar, Chia Seeds (1%), Mineral Salt (341), Natural Sweeteners (Steviol Glycosides, Thaumatin).
